        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Bayesian phylogenetic tree based on partial sequences of the COI gene. Figures on nodes are posterior probabilities, scale bar show branch lengths. Species names followed by geographical range (Indo-Pacific distributions taken from Too et al. 2014; Gosliner et al. 2015)." ;
