<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4779857>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Atys jeffreysi. (a) Apertural view (left image) and adpertural view (right image) of syntype of Bulla (Cylichna) jeffreysi (NHMUK 196472, H = 5.1 mm). (b) Illustration of one of the syntypes taken from Jeffreys (1856: pl. 2, figures 18, 19); apertural view (left image) and adpertural view (right image). (c) Complete shell and shell fragments of syntypes (NHMUK 196472) and accompanying labels (the authorship of B. ovulata is wrongly attributed to Lamarck 1804 in the label). Scale bar = 5 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4779857/files/figure.png" .

